## Workflows
- `quality-gate-iec62304` — Pre-merge quality gate
- `workflow-change-control` — ISO 13485 change control

## Enforcement Scripts
```bash
# Check engines are pure Python
bash .agents/scripts/check_pure_python.sh

# Verify 100% test coverage
python3 .agents/scripts/check_test_coverage.py

# Verify risk file sync
python3 .agents/scripts/check_risk_sync.py
```

## Code Style
- No comments unless asked
- Concise, direct code
- Follow existing patterns exactly
- Type hints required for all public APIs
- Pydantic V2 for all schemas
